This model works well with most anime-style drawings. Basic tags include “best quality,” “masterpiece,” “illustration,” “1girl,” “solo,” “full body,” “Fox ears,” “Mecha,” “machine,” “Bushy tail,” and “Blank background”.

If you want to add mechanical elements to the character’s body, please add “Mechanical body” and use various color tags to change the basic color tone.

If you prefer a simple background, please add “(Mechanical background:1.5)” in the negative tags and adjust the weight to adjust the background.

We welcome everyone to provide feedback and suggestions.

Tsurime eyes - a particular style of drawing eyes in Anime where the outer corners point upward, ending in a distinct point, used in contrast to the traditional Moe Moe soft drooping style,

Tsurime symbolizes strong will, arrogance, or pride in a character. Most noticeable in female designs (since it plays against the stereotype) and is commonly an attribute of tsunderes, kuuderes and particularly badass action girls.

items.name: Amaranth
items.description:
What is Amaranth?

Amaranth is primarily designed for Role Playing Game (RPG) character creations, but it can also do a lot of things like the general stuffs. So basically, it is also great for general use in the realistic or photorealistic image generations. I personally use this model for my works, which is well suited on one of my styles. Regarding text prompts, just be versatile and let your imagination flow.  And, just like most models it also has few issues with the hands, which can be easily mitigated with this model's inpainting (download separately) or some embeddings. (I still have other models, for some specific arts, yet to be released. Your support will go a long way, and a cup of coffee will keep me awake for many nights. Thank you in advance!)

This version of Amaranth does not include a VAE because the goal is for art versatility, wherein, you can use any VAE you like to produce unique aesthetics. Below are the recommended VAEs that you can use with this model to tweak a unique output.

Popular Variable Auto Encoder (VAE)

kl-f8-anime2 VAE (for anime)

anything VAE aka orangemix VAE (for anime)

blessed VAE (for anime)

vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realism)

Sample images above were created with simple text prompts around default settings. More detailed prompts will produce much better results. As for text prompts, just let your imagination flow. One thing to take note, adding keywords like realistic, realism, photorealism, photorealistic, hyperrealism, hyper realistic etc. will make the image more real, and not including any word with real on them will make it look anime-ish.

Settings:

Sampling Method: Euler (realistic) or Euler A (anime)

Sampling Steps: 20 to 30

Resolution: 512x512, 512x768, 768x512

CFG Scale: 4 to 7

Popular Embeddings Used:

Easy Negative

Deep Negative

Bad artist Negative embedding

veryBadImageNegative

bad_prompt Negative Embedding

negative_hand Negative Embedding

EnvyBetterHands LoCon

Detail Tweaker LoRA

SXZ Vivid Darkness

Theovercomer8's Contrast Fix

Limitations:

Do use this model within the boundaries of legalities; do not use it to harm people and entities, or any illegal matters. Using this model means that you alone are responsible for any forms of consequences good or bad, and the author has no liabilities. We all know that AI models can produce both safe and unsafe images for work, so be very responsible.  For all other matters do read the CreativeML-OpenRail-M license Other than that, enjoy using this model and I hope this will help you in your endeavours as an artist.

Support:

First of all, thank you for patronizing this model; it means my efforts didn't go to waste. My goal is to produce more free tools not just for myself and my work, but for others too. Your generosity will go more than a mile. Also, as an artist, writer, programmer, and overall freelancer, I accept commission job. Thank you so much for your support!

items.name: Dryad

Trained on a dataset of women made from plants and trees. Prompt using dryad. Can use green skin, plant girl, or tree legs to generate more plant-like subjects. Use antlers or horns to reduce branch growth on the head.

Due to the small size of the dataset and that it contains a high amount of characters with black sclera or unusual eyes, you may want to use prompts that help increase focus on the eyes like green eyes or looking at viewer.

Most of the dataset contained shots facing the viewer, however, several images were included from behind. Therefore it is possible to do from behind but some additional tweaking may be necessary.

Pictures included were done using either Grapefruit or Meinamix.

这个 Lora 可以生成从后方视角观看的 all fours 姿势的图像。

————————————————————————————————————

trigger word: all fours, from behind <lora:eropose_allfours:0.5>.

The recommended aspect ratios for the images are 3:4, 3:2, 1:1, 2:3, and 3:4.

It produces positive effects from weight 0.3, you can also try weight 0.5, 0.8, or 1.

Due to the training dataset consisting of the same face, the generated face lack variation. You need to add specific facial prompts to alter the face.

items.description:
中文：

关于生命起源，科学家们提出了许多不同的理论来试图理解生命最初是如何出现的。而其中一种"lipid world" theory ,该理论假设生命起源于脂质形成膜，然后将物质和营养物质包裹起来。生物细胞本质上是膜中的膜!

此模型可以用来生成类似的概念图，以及生成一些海洋微生物，原图来自于aBiogenesis on Behancede 的一篇文章，感兴趣的朋友可以自行翻阅。

English:

Abiogenesis is the study of how life originated on Earth. It is a complex and mysterious subject, and scientists have proposed many different theories to try to understand how life first emerged.

Presented here is a conceptual reimagining of the "lipid world" theory which postulates that life originated from lipids forming membranes which would then envelop matter and nutrients. Biological cells are essentially membranes within membranes!

This model can be used to generate similar concept maps, as well as generate some Marine microbes, from an article by aBiogenesis on Behancede, which interested friends can read on their own.

items.name: DIvineAnimeMix
items.description:
If you ran into any troubles with my mix, please read description below. There is plenty of useful information.

Also try: DivineEleganceMix!

Updates:

  • 23.06.2023 - DivineAnimeMix released.

  • 23.06.2023 - Preview images: loading...

Introduction:

DivineAnimeMix, obviously, more anime-styled version of DivineEleganceMix, that was inspired by more clean and straight-forward anime style.

It's still keeps detailed look of original mix, but also has it's own more unique and anime-ish faces and character appearance in general.

  • Clean and sharp anime style

  • Almost post-processing-less generations (if not prompted)

  • Gread prompt guidance

  • Great character and concept recognition

  • Great LoRA (nai/any-based) compatibility

I hope you also would like DivineAnime, so stay tuned for newer versions of mix!

For those, who's curious, why there is "anyshitcocoa_ws03" on the preview images or different hashes. "anyshitcocoa_ws03" is a technical name of the mix and hash is different because i've converted and reuploaded model to .safetensors file. I wouldn't do the same mistake on next mix version. If you unsure if i telling truth, just test the same prompt and seed with uploaded file. Thanks.

Recommendations:

  • Use danbooru tagging for prompts

  • Sampler: Euler at / 30-50 steps

  • Sampler: UniPC at 50+ steps

  • Cfg scale: 8

  • Clip Skip: 2 <---- VERY IMPORTANT

  • ENSD (Eta noise seed delta) - leave blank

  • kl-f8-anime2 VAE

Recommendations (Hires Fix):

  • Upscaler: Fatal Anime

  • Hires steps: 10-15

  • Denoising strength: 0.35

  • Denoising strength (Latent): 0.5

  • Upscale by: any

Models used for mix:

  • Anything v5

  • SenzusHolyshit

  • Cocoa

Troubleshoot:

My colored are bleached out. What should i do?

  • You're missing a VAE file. For this mix i would recommend kl-f8-anime2 VAE. Just put it into SD folder -> models -> VAE folder. Then go to your WebUI, Settings -> Stable Diffusion on the left list -> SD VAE, choose your downloaded vae.

Be aware! Don't use EasyNegative with Style LoRAs, it may ruin the style!

If you're ran into any problem with my mix, you can dm me on discord:

troubledarkness, - discord nickaname

I'll be glad to help | Буду рад помочь.

Really BIG thanks to:

  • andite for Cocoa

  • Linaqruf for original Anything model

  • You, for reading, downloading and reviewing this mix

items.name: Brightness Adjustment_B_1.1|밝기 조정|明度調整
items.description:
My friend wanted a way to adjust only the dark areas of the image without altering the bright areas too much. They also wanted to create a "LORA" that wouldn't heavily modify the overall image. So, they made this. It has a noticeable effect in the range of -1 to 1. Negative values can brighten the dark areas, while positive values can deepen the shadows. It can be used in both real-life and animated settings. If there are any issues with the image, please try adjusting the "LoRA Block Weight" or enlarging the picture. Please use it in compliance with the laws of your region, refrain from causing harm to others, and avoid any illegal activities. If you have any improvement ideas for this LORA, feel free to leave a comment.

내 친구는 밝은 부분을 너무 많이 바꾸지 않고 어두운 영역만 조절할 수 있는 방법을 원했습니다. 또한, 전체적인 화면을 너무 많이 변경하지 않는 "LORA"를 만들고 싶어서 이렇게 만들었습니다. -1에서 1 사이에는 뚜렷한 효과가 있습니다. 음수 값은 어두운 영역을 밝게하고, 양수 값은 그림자를 깊게 할 수 있습니다. 실사나 애니메이션 모두에서 사용할 수 있습니다. 이미지에 문제가 있는 경우에는 "LoRA Block Weight"를 조정하거나 이미지를 확대해 보십시오. 사용은 귀하의 지역 법률을 준수하고, 다른 사람에게 해를 입히지 않으며, 불법 활동을 피하십시오. 이 LORA에 대한 개선 아이디어가 있다면 언제든지 의견을 남겨 주십시오.

私の友人は、画面の暗い部分だけを調整し、明るい部分をあまり変えない方法を望んでいました。 また、画面全体をあまり変更しない"LORA"を作りたかったので、これを作成しました。 -1から1までの範囲で明確な効果があります。負の値は暗い領域を明るくし、正の値は暗い領域を深くすることができます。 リアルな映像やアニメーションに使用することができます。 画面に問題がある場合は、「LoRA Block Weight」を調整するか、画像を拡大してみてください。 使用する際は、ご自身の地域の法律を守り、他人に害を与えず、違法行為を行わないでください。このLORAに改善のアイデアがあれば、コメントを残してください。

我的朋友希望有一個只調整畫面暗區而不改變亮區太多明暗

並且也不會改變太多畫面的"LORA"所以製作了這個

在-1~1都有明顯的效果 負值可以照亮暗區正直可以加深暗區

可以在真實或者動漫類型中使用 使用如果有畫面破損,請嘗試“LoRA Block Weight”進行調整或者將圖片放大 使用請遵守你所在地區法律,不要傷害他人並且違法 如果對此LORA有改進的想法歡迎你留言

亮度调整 我的朋友希望有一个只调整画面暗区而不改变亮区太多明暗的方式。 同时也不会对画面做太多改变的"LORA"，所以制作了这个。 在-1到1之间都有明显的效果，负值可以照亮暗区，正值可以加深暗区。 可以在真实或动漫类型中使用。使用时如果有画面破损，请尝试调整"LoRA Block Weight"进行调整或将图片放大。 使用时请遵守您所在地区的法律，不要伤害他人并且违法。如果对这个LORA有改进的想法，欢迎留言。

"Brightness Control_L_1.1"

This is an additional feature of Brightness Control. It only makes minor adjustments to the bright areas of the image. When using a positive value, it brightens the bright areas, and when using a negative value, it reduces the intensity of the bright areas.

これは明るさ調整の追加機能です。画面の明るい部分の微調整を行います。正の値を使用すると、明るい部分が明るくなり、負の値を使用すると、明るい部分の強度が低くなります。

이것은 밝기 조절의 보충 기능입니다. 그것은 화면의 밝은 부분에만 미세한 조정을 가합니다. 양수 값을 사용하면 밝은 부분이 더 밝아지고, 음수 값을 사용하면 밝은 부분의 강도가 약해집니다.

這是Brightness Control 的補充功能 他只對畫面亮部做微調 正值的時候加亮亮部,負值的時候減弱亮部

这是Brightness Control 的补充功能 他只对画面亮部做微调 正值的时候加亮亮部,负值的时候减弱亮部

items.name: Frank Gallagher from "Shameless"
items.description:
Francis "Frank" Gallagher (William H. Macy and, in flashbacks, Jacob DeMonte-Finn) is the father of six children. He is a deadbeat alcoholic and drug addict who relies on his children to get by. He also swindles the state welfare system and taught this type of opportunistic deceit to his children. Since Frank refuses to work and most of the children are underage, the family lives far below the federal poverty threshold for a family of their size. As mentioned by one of his sons, Lip, Frank is intelligent and finished high school before he attended college to study psychology, where he met Monica. They dated for about 2 weeks before he dropped out of school and they got married.

Frank has sex with almost any available woman to support himself. For instance, he begins a relationship with Sheila Jackson when he discovers that she gets maximum disability benefits for her agoraphobia. He is the biological father of Sammi, Fiona, Lip, Debbie, Carl, and Liam, but not to Ian, who is presumed to be the son of Frank's brother Clayton, making him Frank's nephew as well as the children's half-brother and cousin. Despite that, he refers to Ian as his son. Frank is also the grandfather of Chuckie, Frances, Fred, and Carl's unnamed twins (caused by another scam by Frank).

items.name: ClayMaterial-以兽人为主的粘土手办风格/A clay handmade style dominated by orcs
items.description:
这是一个兽人手办风格，你可以任意替换动物的特征制作不同的兽人。

经过测试后，在写实模型上质感较好，在2.5D模型上有些平面化，但我测试的不多，你可以用在自己喜欢的模型上尝试。

制作完成后，我也尝试了人类角色，但由于数据集中只包含兽人，人类的脸部和质感并不是很好，但也会有一定效果，比如写实模型的2.5D化。

关于提示词，可以使用“fighting stance”制作打斗动作，其他的就看大家的想象力了。

上传的图片包含prompt和模型，可以参考。

Translation:

This is an orc figurine style, and you can replace the animal features to create different orc variations.

After testing, it has a good texture on realistic models, but it appears somewhat flat on 2.5D models. However, I haven't conducted extensive testing, so you can try it on the models you prefer.

After completing the creation, I also attempted human characters. However, since the dataset only includes orcs, the facial features and texture for humans are not as good. Nevertheless, it still produces some effects, such as a 2.5D representation of a realistic model.

For prompts, you can use "fighting stance" to create combat actions, and the rest depends on everyone's imagination.

The uploaded images include prompts and the model for reference.
